s="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 13:13:13 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2023/aug/12/woman-charged-with-after-dog-walker-stabbed-in-sheffield-park" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/business/2023/aug/12/bailiffs-making-record-profits-collecting-debt-for-councils-in-cost-of-living-crisis" target="_blank">Bailiffs making record profits collecting debt for councils in cost of living crisis</a></h2><div class="description"> Newlyn Group is hired by councils to recover unpaid traffic fines and council tax. Its turnover from debt collection increased by 43.8% to £25.8m in the year to December 2022. Company documents describe the figures as Newlyn’s ‘best ever results’</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 13:23:37 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">health</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/business/2023/aug/12/bailiffs-making-record-profits-collecting-debt-for-councils-in-cost-of-living-crisis" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2023/aug/12/ai-could-have-bigger-impact-on-uk-than-industrial-revolution-says-dowden" target="_blank">AI could have bigger impact on UK than Industrial Revolution, says Dowden</a></h2><div class="description"> Deputy PM says technology may aid faster government decisions - but warns of massive hacking risks. Oliver Dowden said AI could speed up productivity and perform boring jobs. But he warned it could be used by hackers to access sensitive information from the government. He said it could have a more significant impact on Britain than the Industrial Revolution.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 12:24:46 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2023/aug/12/ai-could-have-bigger-impact-on-uk-than-industrial-revolution-says-dowden" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/science/2023/aug/12/perseids-meteor-shower-peak" target="_blank">‘Like a ball of fire’: Perseids meteor shower to peak this weekend</a></h2><div class="description"> Perseids will be most visible in northern hemisphere this Saturday and Sunday. The Perseids are named after the Greek hero Perseus because the meteor shower appears to come from the eponymous constellation. While meteors are active from July, Perseids can be seen from July.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 04:00:07 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/science/2023/aug/12/perseids-meteor-shower-peak" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/media/2023/aug/12/virgin-media-customers-threaten-to-not-renew-deals-over-email-problems" target="_blank">Virgin Media customers threaten to not renew deals over email problems</a></h2><div class="description"> Some broadband consumers still cannot access messages or old emails have yet to be restored. Virgin Media customers say they have found themselves in this summer. Some are so furious they are threatening to not renew their broadband contracts. Some customers are still unable to access emails or emails that have been emailed over.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 06:00:10 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/media/2023/aug/12/virgin-media-customers-threaten-to-not-renew-deals-over-email-problems" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2023/aug/11/jeremy-hunts-brother-charlie-dies-of-cancer-aged-53" target="_blank">Jeremy Hunt’s brother, Charlie, dies of cancer aged 53</a></h2><div class="description"> Charlie Hunt discovered he had sarcoma, an aggressive and rare type of cancer that typically begins in the bones or soft tissue, in 2020. Chancellor’s younger brother was diagnosed with the cancer three years ago. Charlie Hunt, 53, has died aged 53 after being diagnosed with cancer.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Fri, 11 Aug 2023 21:51:40 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2023/aug/11/jeremy-hunts-brother-charlie-dies-of-cancer-aged-53" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/12/hawaii-fire-lahaina-maui" target="_blank">Hawaii: growing threat of ‘devastating’ fires as island landscape dries and warms</a></h2><div class="description"> Maui's historic town of Lahaina has been hit by a series of wildfires in recent years. The island's landscapes have dried and warmed, creating tinderbox conditions as the island’s landscapes dry and warmed. Invasive grasses that are primed to burn are causing the fires to flare up in western Maui.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 11:00:16 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/12/hawaii-fire-lahaina-maui" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/12/georgia-da-fani-willis-summons-trump-election-inquiry" target="_blank">Georgia DA summons former lawmaker and journalist in Trump election inquiry</a></h2><div class="description"> Fani Willis’s office has issued summonses to former Georgia lieutenant governor Geoff Duncan and journalist George Chidi to testify before a grand jury on Tuesday. Duncan and Chidi will testify about Donald Trump's alleged efforts to overturn the 2020 presidential election results in that state. Prosecutors could ask the grand jury to hand up charges as well.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 12 Aug 2023 21:48:26 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/12/georgia-da-fani-willis-summons-trump-election-inquiry" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a>